<p class="p2">2007, 2008<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>Till Bovermann (Bielefeld University)</p>
<p class="p4"><br></p>
<p class="p2">implements <a href="JInT.html"><span class="s1">JInT</span></a> for a Wacom Tablet (supported: Intuos, Graphire, Bamboo)</p>
